@startuml
actor Penjual
participant "View" as V
participant "Routes" as R
participant "ReportController" as C
participant "Database" as M
participant "Excel Package" as E

Penjual -> V : Membuka halaman Dashboard Utama (Penjual)
V -> R : GET /seller/dashboard
R -> C : dashboard()
C -> M : Hitung total omset, jumlah pesanan,\ndan daftar produk terlaris milik toko
M --> C : Data Statistik
C --> V : Render grafik (Line chart & Bar chart)
V --> Penjual : Tampilkan ringkasan metrik
Penjual -> V : Membuka menu "Laporan Penjualan"
Penjual -> V : Memilih filter rentang tanggal (Start Date - End Date)
Penjual -> V : Menekan tombol "Export Excel"
V -> R : GET /seller/reports/sales/export?start=...&end=...
R -> C : exportExcel()
C -> M : Query data transaksi berstatus "Selesai"\nberdasarkan filter waktu
M --> C : Data Transaksi
C -> C : Mempersiapkan layout file Excel\n(produk, qty, harga, ongkir, komisi platform)
C -> E : Generate file .xlsx (Laravel Excel)
E --> C : File Excel
C --> Penjual : Kirim file ke browser (Download)
@enduml
